From: NelloKudo <marshnelloosu@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Mar 2026 21:11:43 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Add fix for Persona5: The Phantom X (Global)

Needs gamedrive fix to detect proper install space.
---
 gamefixes-steam/3061570.py | 7 +++++++
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 gamefixes-steam/3061570.py

diff --git a/gamefixes-steam/3061570.py b/gamefixes-steam/3061570.py
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..af09e7d
--- /dev/null
+++ b/gamefixes-steam/3061570.py
@@ -0,0 +1,7 @@
+"""Game fix for Persona5: The Phantom X"""
+
+from protonfixes import util
+
+def early() ->  None:
+    """Needs gamedrive fix to detect proper install space"""
+    util.set_environment('PROTON_SET_GAME_DRIVE', '1')
